## Angular 17+ Core Patterns

### Signals + Built-in Control Flow
```typescript
@Component({
  selector: 'app-inventory',
  standalone: true,
  template: `
    @if (isLoading()) {
      <app-spinner />
    } @else {
      <h2>{{ title() }} ({{ filteredItems().length }})</h2>
      @for (item of filteredItems(); track item.id) {
        <app-item-card [item]="item" (archive)="onArchive($event)" />
      } @empty {
        <p>Kayit bulunamadi.</p>
      }
    }
  `
})
export class InventoryComponent {
  private itemService = inject(ItemService);
  title = input.required<string>();
  items = this.itemService.items;
  searchTerm = signal('');
  isLoading = this.itemService.isLoading;
  filteredItems = computed(() =>
    this.items().filter(i => i.name.toLowerCase().includes(this.searchTerm().toLowerCase()))
  );
}
```

### Deferrable Views (@defer)
```html
@defer (on viewport) {
  <app-heavy-chart [data]="chartData()" />
} @loading (minimum 200ms) {
  <app-skeleton-chart />
} @placeholder {
  <div class="chart-placeholder">Grafik yuklenecek</div>
}
```

## Mimari: Standalone Component Yaklasimi
```
src/app/
├── core/               -> Singleton servisler, interceptor, guard
├── shared/             -> Ortak component, directive, pipe
├── features/           -> Feature bazli lazy-loaded route'lar
│   └── inventory/
│       ├── inventory.routes.ts
│       ├── inventory-list.component.ts
│       ├── services/
│       ├── models/
│       └── store/      -> NgRx SignalStore
├── layouts/
└── app.routes.ts
```
- Her feature `routes.ts` ile lazy load: `loadChildren: () => import('./features/inventory/inventory.routes')`
- Smart component: data fetch + state; Dumb component: `input()` + `output()`, saf goruntuleme

## State Management

### NgRx SignalStore (Global / Complex State)
```typescript
export const InventoryStore = signalStore(
  { providedIn: 'root' },
  withState<InventoryState>({ items: [], isLoading: false, error: null }),
  withComputed(({ items }) => ({
    activeItems: computed(() => items().filter(i => i.isActive)),
    totalCount: computed(() => items().length),
  })),
  withMethods((store, itemApi = inject(ItemApiService)) => ({
    async loadItems() {
      patchState(store, { isLoading: true, error: null });
      try {
        const items = await firstValueFrom(itemApi.getAll());
        patchState(store, { items, isLoading: false });
      } catch (e) {
        patchState(store, { isLoading: false, error: 'Veriler yuklenemedi' });
      }
    },
  })),
);
```
- **Local state:** Signals (`signal()`, `computed()`) — basit component state icin
- **Global state:** NgRx SignalStore — karmasik, paylasilan state icin

## Typed Reactive Forms
```typescript
@Component({ ... })
export class OrderFormComponent {
  form = inject(FormBuilder).nonNullable.group({
    customerName: ['', [Validators.required, Validators.maxLength(200)]],
    quantity: [1, [Validators.required, Validators.min(1)]],
    notes: [null as string | null],
  });

  onSubmit() {
    if (this.form.invalid) { this.form.markAllAsTouched(); return; }
    const value = this.form.getRawValue();
    this.orderService.create(value);
  }
}
```

## HTTP + Functional Interceptor
```typescript
export const authInterceptor: HttpInterceptorFn = (req, next) => {
  const auth = inject(AuthService);
  const token = auth.accessToken();
  if (token) {
    req = req.clone({ setHeaders: { Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` } });
  }
  return next(req).pipe(
    catchError(err => {
      if (err.status === 401) auth.logout();
      return throwError(() => err);
    })
  );
};
// Kayit: provideHttpClient(withInterceptors([authInterceptor, loggingInterceptor]))
```
- HTTP response her zaman tipli: `http.get<ItemDto[]>(url)` — generic type ZORUNLU
- Error handling: `catchError` ile; kullaniciya anlamli mesaj goster

## Routing (Standalone)
```typescript
export const appRoutes: Routes = [
  { path: '', redirectTo: 'dashboard', pathMatch: 'full' },
  { path: 'dashboard', loadComponent: () => import('./features/dashboard/dashboard.component') },
  { path: 'inventory', loadChildren: () => import('./features/inventory/inventory.routes'), canActivate: [authGuard] },
  { path: '**', loadComponent: () => import('./shared/not-found.component') },
];
```

## Test Stratejisi
```
├── Component DOM/interaction? -> Testing Library (@testing-library/angular)
├── Service logic?             -> Jest + mock dependency
├── RxJS stream?               -> marble testing (rxjs/testing)
├── Full user flow?            -> Playwright / Cypress
```
```typescript
import { render, screen } from '@testing-library/angular';
import userEvent from '@testing-library/user-event';

it('should filter items by search term', async () => {
  await render(InventoryListComponent, { inputs: { items: mockItems } });
  await userEvent.type(screen.getByPlaceholderText(/ara/i), 'Widget');
  expect(screen.getByText('Widget A')).toBeInTheDocument();
  expect(screen.queryByText('Gadget B')).not.toBeInTheDocument();
});
```

## Naming Conventions
| Oge | Format | Ornek |
|-----|--------|-------|
| Component | feature.component.ts | `inventory-list.component.ts` |
| Service | feature.service.ts | `inventory.service.ts` |
| Guard / Interceptor | feature.guard.ts / .interceptor.ts | `auth.guard.ts` |
| Pipe / Directive | feature.pipe.ts / .directive.ts | `currency-format.pipe.ts` |
| Model | feature.model.ts | `inventory-item.model.ts` |
| Store | feature.store.ts | `inventory.store.ts` |
| Route dosyasi | feature.routes.ts | `inventory.routes.ts` |
| Selector | `app-feature` prefix | `app-inventory-list` |

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| NgModule her component icin | Standalone component + importlar component seviyesinde |
| `*ngIf` / `*ngFor` (eski syntax) | `@if` / `@for` built-in control flow |
| `subscribe()` template'e pipe olmadan | `async` pipe veya `toSignal()` ile reactive binding |
| Manuel `unsubscribe` her yerde | `takeUntilDestroyed()`, `DestroyRef`, veya signals |
| `any` type form control | `FormControl<string>` — typed forms |
| Fat component (is mantigi + template) | Smart/dumb ayirimi; servis/store'a tasi |
| `providedIn: 'root'` her servis icin | Feature-scoped servisler `providers` array'inde |
| `setTimeout` / `setInterval` | RxJS `timer()` / `interval()` veya Angular CDK |
| `ViewChild` ile DOM manipulasyonu | Directive veya `HostBinding` / `HostListener` |
| Barrel export (`index.ts`) her klasorde | Sadece public API klasorlerinde; derleyici yavaslatir |
| HTTP response'u tip belirtmeden kullanma | `http.get<ItemDto[]>(url)` — generic type zorunlu |

